=> Using in-memory maps is fast but not persistent.
In production, I would replace these with Redis for persistence, high availability, and horizontal scaling.
=> I kept expiration and click count inside UrlMapping for simplicity.
If analytics become very complex, we can separate it later.
=> This design is simple, scalable, and supports both auto-generated and custom short URLs."

